<span id="freeTextContainer11619370354053988979">One of the classics. And there&apos;s a good reason this book has been around for 70 years.<br/><br/>Upsides: A sweet story. Wonderful marriage of illustration and text working in concert. A guest cameo from Mike Mulligan and his Steam shovel if you&apos;re paying close enough attention. <br/><br/>Downsides: Your kids might wonder why the hell you are crying your eyes out when the main character of the story is a house.<br/><br/>Well worth your time.</span>
  <span id="freeText11619370354053988979" style="display:none">One of the classics. And there's a good reason this book has been around for 70 years.<br /><br />Upsides: A sweet story. Wonderful marriage of illustration and text working in concert. A guest cameo from Mike Mulligan and his Steam shovel if you're paying close enough attention. <br /><br />Downsides: Your kids might wonder why the hell you are crying your eyes out when the main character of the story is a house.<br /><br />Well worth your time.</span>
