<span id="freeTextContainer14959222284243139969">This is one of the best children&apos;s book I have ever read!<br/>Simple but elegant drawings and simple but meaningful wordings.<br/><br/>The little house lives happily at the countryside, until a highway is built next to it and suddenly the city expands around it.<br/><br/>This book is a wonderful way to show to the little children:<br/>1. How things evolve and nothing stays the same for long.<br/>2. The fact that no matter how things change, you still can choose a different way.<br/><br/>Little house was sad and lost for a while, but it was</span>
  <span id="freeText14959222284243139969" style="display:none">This is one of the best children's book I have ever read!<br />Simple but elegant drawings and simple but meaningful wordings.<br /><br />The little house lives happily at the countryside, until a highway is built next to it and suddenly the city expands around it.<br /><br />This book is a wonderful way to show to the little children:<br />1. How things evolve and nothing stays the same for long.<br />2. The fact that no matter how things change, you still can choose a different way.<br /><br />Little house was sad and lost for a while, but it was moved again back to countryside by people who cared and understood the importance and uniqueness of its existence.</span>
